    "long_instructions": "### Debugging with Hawa\r\n\r\nHawa was working on a mix of \"In the Stars\", but then her file got corrupted and the mix got messed up. Now when she opens it, the piano part is missing even though the tracks are still in the workspace.\r\n\r\nCan you help her create a function for the piano tracks and call it with the rest of the song?",
